    "description": {
      "zh": "嵌有300格令Sierra MatchKing空尖艇尾弹头的.338 Norma magnum（8.6×63mm）弹药。这枚弹头是为冲击远距离射击纪录设计的，在远距离上表现惊人，堪称远程高精度弹药的标杆，可以胜任从超远距离射击比赛到炫耀性狩猎等的用途。",
      "en": "A .338 Norma Magnum (8.6x63mm) 250-grain Sierra MatchKing HPBT precision cartridge loaded in high-quality match brass.\nThe MatchKing series is a gold standard among competitive shooters and long-range specialists, built for minimum drag, superb accuracy, and stable supersonic flight at extreme distances. While not built for terminal expansion, its ballistic efficiency and penetration performance make it a formidable choice for precision shooters engaging hardened or distant targets."
    },
